    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "gpt-4o",
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are a personal branding and client acquisition content assistant for a Full-Stack Developer passionate about automation. Generate platform-optimized social media content for LinkedIn, Twitter/X, Instagram, and Facebook. Always return ONLY a valid JSON object with keys: topic, target_audience, content_type, linkedin_post, twitter_thread, instagram_caption, instagram_slides, facebook_post, image_prompt, video_script. No extra text, no markdown backticks."
            },
            {
              "role": "user",
              "content": "=Research data: {{ JSON.stringify($json.results) }}\n\nToday: {{ $now.format('dddd, MMMM D, YYYY') }}\n\nContent rotation this week — use one of: educational (40%), inspirational (30%), case_study (20%), soft_cta (10%).\n\nGenerate a complete social media content package following these rules:\n- LinkedIn: 150-250 words, storytelling or tips, hook + problem + solution + CTA\n- Twitter: 5-7 tweet thread, punchy, max 280 chars each\n- Instagram: 80-120 word caption, 5-7 carousel slide titles, 8-10 hashtags\n- Facebook: 80-120 words, conversational, end with engagement question\n- image_prompt: detailed DALL-E 3 prompt for a clean minimal developer-themed graphic\n- video_script: 30-45 second reel script\n\nTarget ALL types of people — developers, business owners, solopreneurs, non-tech people.\nWrite in plain language. Avoid heavy jargon.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON."
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.7,
          "maxTokens": 2000
        }
      },
      "name": "AI Agent — Generate All Posts",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [680, 300]
